{"tid":1244585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港視后) 被大陸三毛圍剿， 李佳芯稱問心無愧","createTime":"2019-06-20T03:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T22:25:45.000Z","uid":134071,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"933c9944d54354bc06481a4eb657173de7cefd93","tid":1244585,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190619/59734459\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190619%2F59734459&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbOisLzr3S4L08%2B1QJ77HZeU%3D&h=b17e1f0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190619%2F59734459&h=64c01fa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190619/59734459</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年06月19<br />\n【對號入座】敏感時期微博發言被大陸網民圍剿 李佳芯稱問心無愧<br />\n<br />\n新晉視后李佳芯（Ali）自轉投大台拍劇後，近年人氣越來越旺。近日香港發生不少對大陸來說非常敏感的事件，然而Ali卻在微博兩度抒發感受，結果當然被大陸網民圍攻。<br />\n<br />\nAli最近於微博上發表兩則帖文，分別為留言：「同學們考試加油！人生旅途上，太多的考驗與試煉，在等待着我們！」另一則是：「內心是甚麼，所看出的便是甚麼。每當遇事不順心，看人不順眼，想想道路之闊窄多寡，在於心胸。少一點憎惡，多一點愛心，世界也因而漂亮。有時候，扭曲了的不是世界、是人心。Darkness cannot drive out darkness; only light can do that. Hate cannot drive out hate; only love can do that.」有大陸網民看到Ali的留言後，對號入座將她定性為「港獨」。<br />\n<br />\n昨日Ali出席劇集宣傳活動時，被問及會否減少在社交網站發佈此類訊息？Ali表示自己一向都有在社交平台抒發個人情感，亦不時會發佈感性留言，她認為現在是敏感時期，所以無論發表甚麼都會被「對號入座」，不同心態的人會用不同角度理解她的說話，而她亦無法控制別人的看法。Ali坦言自己問心無愧，不需要作任何解釋，又表示自己一向如此，為何至今才會被「清算」？Ali說身為藝人，少不免會身處尷尬位置，如今惟有減少在微博的活躍程度，轉而在其他社交網站繼續抒發情感。<br />\n<br />\n而今日Ali亦在IG上呼籲大家要登記做選民，「盡公民責任，把票留在自己手，我已核實選民登記身份。截止日期為7月2日。#奉政府呼籲」而馮盈盈亦留言：「我愛Ali！我愛Ali！I love Ali as much as I love Hong Kong.」"},{"pid":"df4cf5e17f5040625b15a6acdba7e1a51a894c14","tid":1244585,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7935be0602d2f4a31a0cec9eb3e8ea3ad3d8ff46","tid":1244585,"uid":155818,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"李佳芯又真係無乜大陸野<br />\n最大都係Alipay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728002affe5d846df98ad9aaebbf15d34e8e4fed","tid":1244585,"uid":4392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7935be0602d2f4a31a0cec9eb3e8ea3ad3d8ff46","tid":1244585,"uid":155818,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"李佳芯又真係無乜大陸野<br />\n最大都係Alipay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"同埋Alibaba"},{"pid":"0f7ebcedda9924b3545a2412bd67d9ea2268bfab","tid":1244585,"uid":245552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe373a4db9abf31d704cd800563610b3be94eb5","tid":1244585,"uid":19712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7935be0602d2f4a31a0cec9eb3e8ea3ad3d8ff46","tid":1244585,"uid":155818,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"李佳芯又真係無乜大陸野<br />\n最大都係Alipay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:52:22.000Z","msg":"因為佢係Ali<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc14e6eb711728bcde84181eee7a64a65f38452a","tid":1244585,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T03:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65af55130246dba554c34cdca31ba49f4f415003","tid":1244585,"uid":75001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":